{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "第六回\"雅座\"以慕容秋水的暖阁为舞台，展开一段因梦与旧情的纠缠。四年前，慕容秋水在西湖偶遇白衣女子因梦，一夜缱绻后她悄然离去，带走他的玉牌。如今因梦重现，要求慕容秋水兑现承诺——将一个她指定的人送入刑部大牢中最黑暗恐怖的\"雅座\"囚室，让此人求生不得求死不能，整整两年七个月一十三天。慕容秋水从因梦口中得知，这一切都是为了花错——一个碧眼雪肤的浪子，因梦的丈夫，已死于刀下。花错身世坎坷，幼时被富孀花雪夫人收养，一生嗜刀如命，终为刀所害。因梦与花错在雪村相识，一见钟情，却也因此树敌无数。慕容秋水答应了因梦的请求，条件是因梦也要对他许下同样的承诺。随后三人前往刑部大牢，会见雅座主人韦好客——一个驼背鸡胸的畸形人，却是鹰爪门最杰出的传人，他对慕容秋水崇拜至极。因梦将一个面目全非的\"贵宾\"交给了韦好客，此人已被诸葛大夫改造得面目全非。最终因梦发誓要活下去复仇，心中已无爱与感激，只剩索讨与报复。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三代为官，才懂得穿衣吃饭。要做一个第一号的花花公子，可不是人人都能做得到的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有的人能吹风，有的人不能。我就是个天生不能吹风的人，老天给我这一身皮肤就是不让我吹风的，那些好风都留给别人去吹吧！我最好还是待在屋子里，喝一盅醇酒，唱一曲新词，让一个漂漂亮亮的小女孩，把一瓣刚剥好的橘子，洒上一点洁白胜雪的吴盐，放到我的嘴巴里去，这样子我才会活得长一些。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "是你？是你来了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "当然是我，当然是我来了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "可是我记得你已经走了。我记得你走的时候，好像连一个字都没有留，一句话都没有说。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "既然要走，还有什么可说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "既然已走，又何必要再来。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "因为一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "什么话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我还记得你曾经答应过我，以后只要我有事要来找你，你一定会为我做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你还记不记得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "我记得。我对你说过的每一句话，我都记得。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你是不是也说过，一个人如果答应了别人一件事，就好像欠下了一笔债？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我记得你说过的话，我也相信，所以今天我才会来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "你今天是要我来还债的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "你要我怎么还？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我曾经听说这个世界上最黑暗最可怕的地方，就是一个叫做'雅座'的小屋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "雅座？雅座怎么会是黑暗恐怖的地方？有时候我也会到饭馆酒楼去，我坐的就是雅座。据我所知，雅座通常都是为贵宾贵客准备的地方。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你什么时候开始学会骗人？据我所知，像你这样的贵公子，通常都不屑于骗人的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "难道你说的雅座还有什么别的意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你应该知道的，在刑部大牢某一个最幽秘阴暗的角落里，有三两间很特别的雅室，是特别为了招待像你这样的大人物请去的贵宾贵客而准备的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我也知道你们特别派到那里去接待宾客的韦好客先生，实在是好客极了，他接待客人的方法，常常令人连作梦都想不到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "据说，有一位已经练成金钟罩铁布衫十三太保横练的江湖好汉，到你们的雅座去作客三天后，出来的时候，想爬到他最喜欢的女人身上都爬不上去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "看起来你知道的事还真不少。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "但是我却不知道，你这次来找我，是想要我把一位贵宾从雅座中请出来呢？还是要我替你把一位贵宾送到雅座里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "有一个人现在我还不想要他死，我至少也要让他再多活两年七个月一十三天。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你一定要答应我，这一段日子一定要在雅座里好好的款待他，让他每天都想死，却又死不了。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "这个人是谁？为什么如此恨他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "其实你不说我也知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "知道什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "花错。你这么样做，当然是为了花错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "花错？你怎么会知道花错？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "我怎么会不知道花错，我从小就是个坏孩子，他甚至比我还坏。我相信这个世界上恐怕再也没有人比我更了解他了，如果不是为了他那种男人，你怎么舍得放弃我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_xue_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "花雪夫人",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "我喜欢你，你是个迷死人的小女孩，可是我劝你现在还是赶快走的好。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_hua_xue_fu_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_xue_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "花雪夫人",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "因为我那个宝贝儿子就快要回来了，你最好还是不要见到他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_hua_xue_fu_ren",
      "text": "我为什么不能见他？难道他会咬我一口？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_xue_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "花雪夫人",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "他不会咬你，他只会把你连皮带骨都吞下。你一定要相信我，这个野孩子天生就有一种吸引女孩子的魅力，甚至在他三岁的时候就已经显露出来了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_xue_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "花雪夫人",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "那时候他正在街上玩泥巴，正好挡住了我的路，我本来想一脚把这个脏孩子踢开的，可是他忽然抬起头来对我笑了笑。就在那一瞬间，这个脏小孩身上的烂泥，好像一下子就忽然不见了，忽然就变成了一个可爱的白玉娃娃。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_hua_xue_fu_ren",
      "text": "所以你立刻就决定收养他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_xue_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "花雪夫人",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "是的。对于这件事，我从来都没有后悔过。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_hua_xue_fu_ren",
      "text": "我做事也从来不会后悔的。如果我遇到一个男人，不管他是谁，被吞下去的，通常都不会是我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是的！我是为了花错。从我第一眼看到他开始，我就知道我是这一生已经属于他了，后来我才知道，当时他也有那种感觉。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "可是就在那一瞬间，我心里也隐约有了一种不祥的预兆，当然我也说不出为了什么，后来我才发现我们的仇敌实在太多了，他的仇敌和我的仇敌。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "你也会有仇敌？我记得你一直都能把每个人都对付得很好的，不管男人女人都一样。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "可是我嫁给他以后就不一样了。这一点你该明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "是的，我完全明白。老实说，当我知道你们两个人已经在一起的时候，甚至连我都有一点恨你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "现在呢？现在你是不是还有一点恨我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "现在没有了，现在我好像已经什么都没有了，好像已经老的可以做祖父了。一个已经做了祖父的人，是不会再吃醋的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你根本就不会吃醋的，没有人会为一个死人吃醋。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "难道花错死了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "每个人都会死。花错至少也是个人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "他怎么死的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "死在刀下。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "为什么喜欢刀的人，通常都会死在刀下？为什么让你伤心的人总是你喜欢的人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "这大概是因为只有你喜欢的人才能伤害到你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "谁说你不喜欢的人就不能伤害你？难道你喜欢杀死花错的那个人，难道他没有伤害到你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "你一定要记住，有些听起来很有学问的话，其实全都是放屁，而且是很臭很臭的屁。所以我们不如开始说一点比较实际的事。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "如果我答应了你的要求，你准备怎么样来报答我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你准备要我怎么报答你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "我只要你的一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "一句什么样的话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "就是我曾经对你说过的那句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你是不是要我答应你，以后只要你有事来找我，我一定都要替你做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "是的。就是这样子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "好，我答应你。只要是我答应过别人的事，我也从来不会忘记的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "那就好极了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "你要交给我的那位贵宾，现在在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你要招待他的雅座，什么时候才能准备好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "三天。最多只要三天。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你有把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "我有。我们雅座的主人韦好客先生，一向是个办事很快的人。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "那就好极了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "三天之内，我就会把那位贵宾交给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "你那位贵宾叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你用不着知道他的名字。你只要记住，他是一位很特别的贵宾就够了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我希望你也让韦好客先生牢记在心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "这位就是雅座的主人韦好客先生。我可以保证他好客的声名绝不假。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我只不过尽力去做而已，只不过希望我的客人们能对我的服务满意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 457
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "只可惜他们好像还是不太喜欢你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "韦先生。我相信你现在一定已经知道：这里又有一位贵宾要来了，而且恐怕会在这里待很久。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "是的。我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "我相信你一定也知道，这位客人是我请来的，我对他当然特别关心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "那么我就想请教你几件事了。他到了这里之后有没有机会逃出去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "大概没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "能够被请到我这里来的贵客，通常都是非常有身份有地位的人，我在这里已经有十一年了，被请来的贵客已经有一百三十多位，我可以保证如果我把他们任何一个人的名字说出来，都会在江湖中引起一场很不小的动乱。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "他们有没有人能逃得出去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "没有。连一个都没有。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "如果他们想死呢？是不是能够死得了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "夫人，你一定要相信我，死并不是一件很容易的事，越想要死的人，往往都越死不了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "夫人，如果你要一个人在我的雅座里待两年七月零一十三天，我绝不会让他少活一个时辰。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "你保证？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "你现在是不是已经对我们这位好客的主人完全满意？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "那么你是不是已经可以把我们那位客人请进来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "夫人，请恕我直言。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "什么话？你说。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "其实你根本不用把这位贵宾请到我这雅座里来，你对他的招待和服务已经是够周到了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 541
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "我承认你说的有理，我把他送到这里，只不过因为我根本没法子招待他那么久，而且我希望他在这里能受到更好的待遇。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "夫人，你知道我一定会尽力去做。还有一件事我也想请教夫人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 549
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "我看得出我们这位贵宾的脸已经被改造过，我已经有多年没有看见过如此精密的手艺，我实在很想知道是哪一位大师的杰作？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 555
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "你真的很想知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "其实你不问也应该知道，除了诸葛大夫之外还有谁？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "诸葛大夫？你说的是诸葛仙？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "不错，我说的就是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "对一个像你这么高贵美丽的女士表示怀疑，实在是件很不礼貌的事，只可惜对你说的话，我想不怀疑都不行。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 575
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_meng",
      "speaker_name": "因梦",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋水",
      "listener": "char_yin_meng",
      "text": "因为我很了解诸葛先生的为人。像这一类的事，他大概是不会做的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 581
    },
    {
